<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">現在這個季節，<delay8 />只要一鬆懈下來，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />立刻就會被周公請去泡茶啊<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />呼啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對我這個容易流汗的人來說，<delay8 />
現在這季節算是挺難受的啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過盡情流汗後
喝的<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />格外美味。<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從這點來看，倒是個好季節啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在這個時期不會太熱<delay8 />也不會太冷，<delay20 />
溫度適中很舒服，不錯耶！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真希望永遠都是這樣的天氣，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在我小的時候啊，<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大人們總是對我說這類的話：<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「手插口袋不禮貌，<delay8 />把手拔出來！」<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是冷就是冷，<delay20 />
用不著勉強自己啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="15" arg="0x6504 0x6600 0xcd00" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我小時候在學校學過一首歌，<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概是「一到夏天就會回想起那風景」<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這類的歌<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然那首歌非常適合合唱啦，<delay40 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是仔細想想，無論歌詞或旋律，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都絲毫沒有夏天的感覺。
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不如說還滿涼爽的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且話說回來，<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />水芭蕉根本不是在<delay8 />夏天開花嘛！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在現在這個季節，<delay20 />
有時會讓我陷入沉思啊。<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎樣啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的背影<delay8 />有滲出
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />憂愁感之類的東西嗎？</message>
	<message label="007_a" attrib="67 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">有喔！</message>
	<message label="007_b" attrib="68 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">什麼都沒有耶</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="69 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">只要天氣一變冷，<delay20 />
就會很想念<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />熱～騰騰的<delay8 />食物啊。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="009_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />春風拂面、氣候宜人，<delay20 />
這時候外出真的很舒服～<delay20 />
真是個最適合散步的季節啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到春天<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
就會想到「開學」、<delay8 />「開工」、<delay8 />「開張」<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這些拉開新生活序幕的事件，<delay8 />對吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我因為在島上悠哉生活，<delay20 />
所以和這些事件徹底無緣就是了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可能是因為氣候回暖了吧？<delay frames="30" />
開始可以頻繁見到昆蟲的身影了。<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />漫天飛舞的蝴蝶可是春季特有的美景，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x6d 0x6e 0x6e 0x6e 0x6f 0x6f" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="011_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">秋意也已經濃啦……<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這秋天<delay8 />對你來說
算是個食慾之秋嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">聽著秋季的蟲鳴，<delay8 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總是會讓人不禁覺得感傷呀，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">如果要享受秋天的雅趣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那當然就是「追楓」啦！<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過呀<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們又不是要把楓樹抓來吃了，<delay20 />
為什麼我們要說「追楓」啊？<delay20 />
真是不可思議，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x70 0x70 0x71 0x71 0x72 0x72" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「春眠不覺曉」！<10_4 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是賴床時<delay8 />非常好用的咒語！<delay40 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然一點效果都沒有啦！<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sneezing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="16" /><10_10 />哈啾！<10_9 /><delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鼻子好癢啊，<delay20 />看來差不多到了
容易出現花粉症症狀的季節嗎？
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />講是這樣講，<delay8 />其實一整年都有各種不同花粉，<delay20 />
所以跟季節也沒什麼關係吧<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Sneezing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="16" /><10_10 />哈啾！<10_9 /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就知道！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真正的男子漢啊，<delay8 />就算沉默不語，
光靠背影也能傳達千言萬語啦！<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀？<delay frames="80" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是假裝<delay8 />在思考，<delay20 />
果然無法傳達任何事啊！<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x6a 0x6b 0x6c" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在鍋子裡翻騰的<delay8 />鍋燒烏龍麵，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺真是超讚的啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呼～～～<delay8 />地吹涼，<delay40 />
接著一鼓作氣把麵吸進嘴裡！<pageBreak /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_10 />好燙燙～～！<delay8 /><10_9 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哼<delay frames="4" />呵<delay frames="4" />吼<delay frames="4" />嚇<delay frames="4" />嘿<delay frames="4" />啊<delay frames="4" />哈<delay frames="4" /><10_5 /><colour id="5" />（根本就還沒涼啊）<colour id="65535" />！<endTag a="10" b="5" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈呼、<delay20 />哈呼<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay8 />真受不了！<delay40 />
講得我肚子都餓啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在鍋子裡翻騰的<delay8 />關東煮，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺真是超讚的啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把煮得非～<delay8 />常入味的蒟蒻<delay8 />
沾滿辣粉，<delay40 />
大口放進嘴裡！<pageBreak /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_10 />好燙燙～～！<delay8 /><10_9 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈<delay frames="4" />呵<delay frames="4" />呼<delay frames="4" />好<delay frames="4" />嘻<delay frames="4" />哈<delay frames="4" />嗨<delay frames="4" />吼<delay frames="4" />呵<delay frames="4" /><10_5 /><colour id="5" />（不小心放太多辣粉了）<colour id="65535" />！<endTag a="10" b="5" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈呼、<delay20 />哈呼<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay8 />真受不了！<delay40 />
講得我肚子都餓啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在鍋子裡翻騰的<delay8 />泡菜豆腐鍋，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺真是超讚的啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呼～～～<delay8 />地吹涼，<delay40 />
再把煮得鮮紅的豆腐送進嘴裡！<pageBreak /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_10 />好燙燙～～！<delay8 /><10_9 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿<delay frames="4" />嘻<delay frames="4" />哈<delay frames="4" />呵<delay frames="4" />嗨<delay frames="4" />哈<delay frames="4" /><10_5 /><colour id="5" />（嘴裡鬧火災啦）<colour id="65535" />！<endTag a="10" b="5" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈呼、<delay20 />哈呼<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay8 />真受不了！<delay40 />
講得我肚子都餓啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">只要在夏天的時候早起，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就會想起<delay8 />小時候每天早上掛著出席卡，<delay20 />
參加收音機體操的回憶啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然當時的我也和現在一樣難以早起，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但因為非常想要拿到最後發的小點心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以總是會在體操結束之前趕到，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽好啦？<delay20 />
這個季節非常炎熱，
別忘了經常補充水分喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像今天這種悶熱的夜晚，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果能大口咬下<delay8 />冰涼涼的西瓜，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那肯定超棒的！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還是說……<delay20 /><anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
你想聽我講個<delay8 />超～級恐怖故事，<delay20 />
讓你嚇得寒毛直豎啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在冬天早上<delay8 />要離開被窩的時候，<delay20 />
非常需要氣勢跟毅力啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每天早上都是一場<delay8 />艱辛的戰鬥咧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />寒冷只要多穿幾件就可以對抗，<delay frames="30" />
但炎熱的時候<delay8 />即使脫個精光，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也沒辦法變得涼爽。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且天氣一熱，<delay8 />就會讓人沒有食慾。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從這點來說，寒冷的冬天會促進食慾，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而冬天的火鍋又美味無比，<delay8 />真的是最棒了！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣一想，<delay8 />
寒～冷的冬天<delay20 />就也沒那麼糟了吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有些人會說<delay20 />
「手越冰的人，內心就越溫暖」……<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開什麼玩笑啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />僅憑手的溫度，
怎麼就能斷定一個人的內心溫不溫暖！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的溫柔啊，<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是要花上許多時間，
才能慢慢傳達給對方的事物！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>